[
  {
    "startTime": 0.5,
    "endTime": 4.15,
    "text": "Last time you were here, you were with--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 4.15,
    "endTime": 4.65,
    "text": "Jason."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 4.65,
    "endTime": 5.130000000000001,
    "text": "Jason, right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 5.13,
    "endTime": 6.463,
    "text": "And you were doing shots, right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.463,
    "endTime": 7.93,
    "text": "You were doing tequila shots."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.93,
    "endTime": 8.43,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.43,
    "endTime": 10.41,
    "text": "Now today you're not going to do tequila shots."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.41,
    "endTime": 11.97,
    "text": "I brought some, just in case you wanted some,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.97,
    "endTime": 13.83,
    "text": "because you said it was on your bucket list"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.83,
    "endTime": 15.3,
    "text": "to do shots with me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.3,
    "endTime": 15.91,
    "text": "Yes, it was."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.91,
    "endTime": 16.47,
    "text": "It was."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.47,
    "endTime": 17.619,
    "text": "So I did that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.62,
    "endTime": 18.48,
    "text": "Thank you very much."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.48,
    "endTime": 20.43,
    "text": "So what else is on your bucket list?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.43,
    "endTime": 22.35,
    "text": "Oh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.35,
    "endTime": 23.1,
    "text": "With me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.1,
    "endTime": 23.64,
    "text": "With you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.64,
    "endTime": 25.41,
    "text": "Let's jump out of an airplane?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.41,
    "endTime": 27.875,
    "text": "But in 30 years, because it can't do it now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.875,
    "endTime": 31.314,
    "text": "No, I used to want to do that, but I can't even"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.314,
    "endTime": 32.189,
    "text": "imagine doing it now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.189,
    "endTime": 33.75,
    "text": "But when I was younger, I thought for sure,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.75,
    "endTime": 35.28,
    "text": "I would one day jump out of an airplane."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.28,
    "endTime": 36.79,
    "text": "It seems like the thing that you want to do, right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.79,
    "endTime": 37.885,
    "text": "Just to have that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.885,
    "endTime": 39.62,
    "text": "Just to have done it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.62,
    "endTime": 40.769,
    "text": "I should have done it before I had a kid."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.77,
    "endTime": 42.900000000000006,
    "text": "Now it just feels like it--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.9,
    "endTime": 43.35,
    "text": "if it went bad, I would--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.35,
    "endTime": 43.83,
    "text": "It'd be irresponsible."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.83,
    "endTime": 44.19,
    "text": "Well, I wouldn't feel bad."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.19,
    "endTime": 44.98,
    "text": "I wouldn't be here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.981,
    "endTime": 47.569,
    "text": "But, I wouldn't want him to feel bad."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.569,
    "endTime": 49.11,
    "text": "So I want to do that, and I really, I"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.11,
    "endTime": 50.318,
    "text": "don't know how to scuba dive."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.318,
    "endTime": 52.172,
    "text": "Like, I've never gone deep scuba diving."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.172,
    "endTime": 53.129,
    "text": "I want to do that, too."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.13,
    "endTime": 54.5,
    "text": "I'll do that with you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.5,
    "endTime": 54.55,
    "text": "Yeah?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.55,
    "endTime": 54.87,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.87,
    "endTime": 55.452,
    "text": "We'll do that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.453,
    "endTime": 58.190000000000005,
    "text": "I do have kind of an irrational fear about the scuba diving, though."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.69,
    "endTime": 59.19,
    "text": "Yeah?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.19,
    "endTime": 61.939,
    "text": "Because you're so far under and you can't breathe?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.939,
    "endTime": 63.73,
    "text": "No, that that's a completely rational fear."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.73,
    "endTime": 66.188,
    "text": "Mine is that the fish are going to decide like, well you've"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.188,
    "endTime": 67.83,
    "text": "eaten enough of us."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.83,
    "endTime": 69.451,
    "text": "Oh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.451,
    "endTime": 69.949,
    "text": "Wow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.95,
    "endTime": 73.37,
    "text": "Just regular fish without teeth will go at you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.37,
    "endTime": 74.51,
    "text": "Like something will happen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.51,
    "endTime": 75.71000000000001,
    "text": "Like we'll have released something in the water,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.71,
    "endTime": 76.699,
    "text": "and they'll just turn."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.7,
    "endTime": 78.2,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.2,
    "endTime": 79.151,
    "text": "And they want revenge."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.151,
    "endTime": 79.649,
    "text": "They would--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.65,
    "endTime": 80.733,
    "text": "And they're coming for me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.733,
    "endTime": 81.74000000000001,
    "text": "I understand."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.74,
    "endTime": 83.83,
    "text": "That is irrational."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.831,
    "endTime": 85.164,
    "text": "It's very irrational."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.164,
    "endTime": 87.8,
    "text": "Because they don't have any teeth or anything,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.8,
    "endTime": 88.964,
    "text": "the kind that people eat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.964,
    "endTime": 90.38,
    "text": "That's why it would be so painful."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.38,
    "endTime": 91.28,
    "text": "Right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.28,
    "endTime": 91.93,
    "text": "They'd gum you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.93,
    "endTime": 93.10000000000001,
    "text": "They'd gum you to death."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.1,
    "endTime": 94.896,
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.896,
    "endTime": 95.8,
    "text": "That tickles."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.8,
    "endTime": 96.661,
    "text": "That tickles."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.661,
    "endTime": 97.16,
    "text": "Stop."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.16,
    "endTime": 98.929,
    "text": "No, wait, ah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.93,
    "endTime": 100.82000000000001,
    "text": "All right, let's talk about Ocean's 8."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.82,
    "endTime": 103.669,
    "text": "There's a great group of women in this movie."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.67,
    "endTime": 105.39,
    "text": "Did you know any of them before?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.39,
    "endTime": 107.607,
    "text": "Yeah, I met a couple of them before."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.607,
    "endTime": 108.44,
    "text": "But it wasn't like--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.44,
    "endTime": 110.0,
    "text": "I wasn't close with anybody."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.0,
    "endTime": 110.99,
    "text": "Now we're all close."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.99,
    "endTime": 111.5,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.5,
    "endTime": 113.28,
    "text": "And who were you closest with?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.28,
    "endTime": 114.44,
    "text": "Now?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.44,
    "endTime": 117.8,
    "text": "All of them."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.8,
    "endTime": 117.8,
    "text": "We really are."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.8,
    "endTime": 120.47,
    "text": "We all-- it just was this huge, huge love"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.47,
    "endTime": 121.387,
    "text": "fest, which was great."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.387,
    "endTime": 123.261,
    "text": "Because there's that terrible rumor out there"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.261,
    "endTime": 124.67,
    "text": "that women can't get along."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.67,
    "endTime": 126.9,
    "text": "And man, did we just murder that rumor."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.9,
    "endTime": 129.5,
    "text": "We just loved each other so much."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.5,
    "endTime": 132.44,
    "text": "And it was so special, like the movie was always going to be significant,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.44,
    "endTime": 135.26,
    "text": "because of what it is, and who's in it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.26,
    "endTime": 136.801,
    "text": "But it was really significant for me,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.801,
    "endTime": 139.73,
    "text": "because it was my first movie after having my son."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.73,
    "endTime": 142.54299999999998,
    "text": "And I'm not somebody--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.544,
    "endTime": 146.31,
    "text": "one of the lucky things about being in this business for so long is that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.36,
    "endTime": 148.318,
    "text": "I've really kind of come to terms with the pressure that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.318,
    "endTime": 149.54000000000002,
    "text": "you get to look a certain way as an actress."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.54,
    "endTime": 152.63,
    "text": "And I don't beat myself up about any of that stuff anymore."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.63,
    "endTime": 155.24,
    "text": "But after I had my son the weight"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 532.2,
    "endTime": 534.589,
    "text": "was really slow to come off."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 534.589,
    "endTime": 535.7600000000001,
    "text": "And so I was a different size than I normally am."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 535.76,
    "endTime": 544.17,
    "text": "And the director told me, like that's great,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 544.17,
    "endTime": 554.03,
    "text": "we have eight women in this movie."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 554.03,
    "endTime": 560.769,
    "text": "We need have as many body types up there as we can,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 560.769,
    "endTime": 569.03,
    "text": "which I was really relieved to hear."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 569.03,
    "endTime": 571.579,
    "text": "But I walked on the set, and like you know,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 571.579,
    "endTime": 579.1999999999999,
    "text": "my weight's a little up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 579.2,
    "endTime": 582.2900000000001,
    "text": "And I'm just aware of it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 582.29,
    "endTime": 587.05,
    "text": "And I walk on the set, and like I'm in my jeans,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 587.05,
    "endTime": 591.12,
    "text": "and I've done my best, and I'm going"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 591.12,
    "endTime": 599.839,
    "text": "to love myself no matter what."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 599.839,
    "endTime": 606.36,
    "text": "And Sandy Bullock just looks up and goes, looking good mama."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 606.36,
    "endTime": 609.86,
    "text": "I was like oh, made me feel amazing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 609.86,
    "endTime": 618.8100000000001,
    "text": "And then Cate Blanchett is like, (AUSTRALIAN ACCENT),"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 618.81,
    "endTime": 624.27,
    "text": "nice jeans, Hathaway."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 624.27,
    "endTime": 630.18,
    "text": "This is so great."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 630.18,
    "endTime": 634.9899999999999,
    "text": "And then Rihanna looks up and goes, damn girl, you got a ass."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 634.99,
    "endTime": 647.1,
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 647.1,
    "endTime": 646.1800000000001,
    "text": "And I, of course, was too freaked out"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 646.18,
    "endTime": 652.3389999999999,
    "text": "and loved it so much."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 652.339,
    "endTime": 660.149,
    "text": "And I was like, really?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 660.149,
    "endTime": 664.589,
    "text": "And she goes, you've got an ass like me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 664.589,
    "endTime": 673.11,
    "text": "And I can honestly say I've never had that experience on a film set before."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 673.11,
    "endTime": 675.0600000000001,
    "text": "Wow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 675.06,
    "endTime": 680.6999999999999,
    "text": "That's fantastic."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 675.06,
    "endTime": 680.6999999999999,
    "text": "They just so beautiful, and to be"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 680.7,
    "endTime": 685.73,
    "text": "surrounded by that much love, and understanding."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 685.73,
    "endTime": 693.72,
    "text": "It was just great."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 693.72,
    "endTime": 696.4200000000001,
    "text": "Well, that's good to hear."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 696.42,
    "endTime": 703.2099999999999,
    "text": "And I really can't wait to see the film,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 703.21,
    "endTime": 707.48,
    "text": "because it looks really, really good."
  }
]